name: edge_worker

,arrayMap(y -> (akamai_edgeworker_eventhandler(y[3])), arrayMap(x -> splitByChar('/', x), arrayPopFront(splitByString('//', ewUsageInfo))))
,arrayMap(y -> (akamai_edgeworker_offreason(y[4])), arrayMap(x -> splitByChar('/', x), arrayPopFront(splitByString('//', ewUsageInfo))))
,arrayMap(y -> (y[5]), arrayMap(x -> splitByChar('/', x), arrayPopFront(splitByString('//', ewUsageInfo))))
,arrayMap(y -> (akamai_edgeworker_status(y[6])), arrayMap(x -> splitByChar('/', x), arrayPopFront(splitByString('//', ewUsageInfo))))
,arrayMap(y -> (y[7]), arrayMap(x -> splitByChar('/', x), arrayPopFront(splitByString('//', ewUsageInfo)))))
